OL,6,FSingle-headline Ofsted grades for
OL,7,Fschools will be scrapped with
OL,8,Fimmediate effect, the Government has
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FPreviously, Ofsted awarded one of four
OL,12,Fheadline grades to schools it
OL,13,Finspects: outstanding, good, requires
OL,14,Fimprovement and inadequate.
OL,16,FThe announcement follows engagement
OL,17,Fwith the sector and family of
OL,18,Fheadteacher Ruth Perry, after a
OL,19,Fcoroner's inquest found the Ofsted
OL,20,Finspection process had contributed to
OL,21,Fher death.
