OL,6,FMrs Perry took her own life after an
OL,7,FOfsted report downgraded her Caversham
OL,8,FPrimary School in Reading from its
OL,9,Fhighest rating, "outstanding", to its
OL,10,Flowest rating, "inadequate", over
OL,11,Fsafeguarding concerns.
OL,13,FMrs Perry's sister, Professor Julia
OL,14,FWaters, said: "We are delighted and
OL,15,Frelieved that the Government has
OL,16,Fdecided to take this important and
OL,17,Flong-overdue step.
